::Aerotaur::
       He glares at Starstorm, tired of waiting.  "I believe you 
misunderstood me.  That was not a request.  That was an instruction."  His 
blasters slide out of the back of his arms as he continues to glare.  "I am 
her bodyguard.  Anyone attempting to keep me from her will be considered a 
threat to her well-being and summarily eliminated.  Am I making myself 
understood?"

--part1_1ab.13a55168.2bd4cb39_boundary
